description: [``botocore``] Providing Tagging support for DomainName in AppSync
[``botocore``] This release adds support for PySpark jobs. Customers can now analyze data by running jobs using approved PySpark analysis templates.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for AVC passthrough, the ability to specify PTS offset without padding, and an A/V segment matching feature.
[``botocore``] Amazon Route 53 now supports the iso-f regions for private DNS Amazon VPCs and cloudwatch healthchecks.
